description:
Today, I wanted to share my Votann Land Fortress with you all! It’s just a “short” 😉 post, but I couldn’t resist showing it off. I was so hyped about the Votann when they were first launched. However, as any hobbyist will agree, it’s easy to get drawn from one project to another as exciting new models are released. I really need to double my efforts and paint more units—a “little” 😉 effort often goes a long way!

The post Showcase: Leagues of Votann Hekaton Land Fortress appeared first on Tale of Painters.
title: Showcase: Leagues of Votann Hekaton Land Fortress
